{
  "stem": "26792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Most of the people who were there did not see sunlight again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't tell you the exact number, but less than a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was just cleaning and washing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody touched me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody called me names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was terribly frightened-- not only to me, to many of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're in the same position.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going to happen, whether they're going to kill us, to rape us, or what.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm, just can't tell you, a group of about 15 to 20, always about the same.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not released.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean from the prefecture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sent home.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sent home.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also in groups.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also in groups.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, the next-- so then, as the newspapers were full of anti-Semitic articles, the Nuremberg laws were also already imposed on the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had no right to use the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No right to buy anything, no food, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No seat at the cinemas, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not using the tram cars, the buses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And wearing the yellow patch on the breast and on the back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they started opening the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, the ghetto was closed on the 25th of October.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But Jewish people, like my family and others, were settled their much earlier, sooner, because the old-- the place where they established the ghetto had been formerly inhabited by very poor Russian people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And these poor Russian people, against their will, of course, were taken, thrown over to Riga, to the beautiful Jewish houses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Jewish people had to settle in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we had to go rather early-- I don't remember now the exact date, but it was early.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were arrested in the Perkonkrust headquarters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was also in July.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
